data.description: Entertainers delight with a gorgeous oasis, includes a pool w/ waterfalls, covered outdoor bar area, with plenty of room for your BBQ pit. Fabulous flowing layout from pool thru french doors into the game room followed by a covered deck and family room with a fireplace. Updates include new roof (Sept 2016), landscape and landscape lighting, closet systems, fresh paint and more. This single story large over sized corner lot is perfect for entertaining.
